<br>
Best way to keep your group alive is mana/wisdom; but you need to stay alive to use all your mana. So if you are decent on resists/hp then sac some of them for wis, if you are low on resists tho sac some wisdom or hps for them(say 170+ buffed is good).<br>
<br>
Personally i wouldnt worry about wis over 200, the cost is too high for half the return(1-200 wis is 12mana per 1 wis i believe, and 201-255 is 6 mana per 1). If you can get extra wisdom over 200 for free then by all means up it.<br>
<br>
Hrmmm, mabye shoot for about 5000+hp buffed, 170+ buffed in the approiate save, and then dump the rest for wisdom if you are low.<br>
<br>
